title: Ep 18: Tortilla Ta-tas
description:
Today's Proceedings:  A woman whose vacuum cleaner retaliated on her own tortilla ta-tas, a dad whose daughter lets him know how unattractive he is, a man whose sexual endurance needed some working on, and a man whose love for his girlfriend required him to facetime in public.  We also dive back into "No Dumb Questions" and discuss if Christian can pronounce his own name correctly.
